                        <h1><a name="7010"></a><a href="/readMore.html?id=7010">Blogs</a></h1>
                        <div class="ItemInfo">Posted on
                           2004-06-07 at
                           08:21:37,
                           <a href="/readMore.html?id=7010">0 messages in 0 threads.</a> Last comment on 7/06/04.
                        </div>
                        <div>If you haven't noticed already the syndication mechanism has changed and the blogs have come online. Rather than fill the
                           news up with "stuff", James and I have decided that it would be more interesting for those who are interested in following
                           what is actually going on at RedBrick to just post in our blogs.
