                        <h1><a name="4029"></a><a href="/readMore.html?id=4029">Book of Tomorrow 5 Update</a></h1>
                        <div class="ItemInfo">Posted on
                           2004-06-05 at
                           06:56:21,
                           <a href="/readMore.html?id=4029">3 messages in 1 threads.</a> Last comment on 12/07/04.
                        </div>
                        <div>Thanks to everyone who submitted articles for Book of Tomorrow 5! Over the next month, I will be editing the submissions for
                           grammar, punctuation, and spelling. By June 30, they will be ready to pass on to content editors. Content editors read articles
                           for consistency with the world of Earthdawn, as well as edit any included rules for appropriateness and balance.
                        </div><br></td>
                  </tr>
