                        <h1><a name="2659"></a><a href="/readMore.html?id=2659">Earthdawn Merchandise Launches!</a></h1>
                        <div class="ItemInfo">Posted on
                           2004-06-01 at
                           08:53:56,
                           <a href="/readMore.html?id=2659">3 messages in 1 threads.</a> Last comment on 2/06/04.
                        </div>
                        <div>June 1, 2004 (AUCKLAND, NZ) - RedBrick Limited, publishers of the forthcoming Earthdawn&reg; Classic&#153; game line for FASA Corporation's
                           fantasy roleplaying game in the Age of Legend, are pleased to announce the opening of an online store, which will offer Earthdawn&reg;
                           fans a wide variety of licensed merchandise through partner CafePress.
                        </div><br></td>
