                     <td width="100%">
                        <h1><a name="2115"></a><a href="/readMore.html?id=2115">RSS support for pushing news items to your doorstep</a></h1>
                        <div class="ItemInfo">Posted on
                           2004-04-27 at
                           09:46:47,
                           <a href="/readMore.html?id=2115">0 messages in 0 threads.</a> Last comment on 27/04/04.
                        </div>
                        <div>For those who are wondering what the "rss feed" option in News is, it is a syndication mechanism that lets the news items
                           be pulled down to your desktop without you having to visit the web site to be kept up to date. A simple reader is at <a href="http://www.sharpreader.net/" target="_blank">Sharp Reader</a> - it requires .NET, but there are quite a few other readers around (I encourage other people to post suggestions). If there
                           are other areas that could benefit from RSS, please let me know and I will consider adding them.
                        </div><br></td>
                  </tr>
