                        <h1><a name="2058"></a><a href="/readMore.html?id=2058">Campaign support now allows deletes</a></h1>
                        <div class="ItemInfo">Posted on
                           2004-04-24 at
                           07:06:17,
                           <a href="/readMore.html?id=2058">2 messages in 1 threads.</a> Last comment on 27/04/04.
                        </div>
                        <div>If you wanted to try the Campaigns stuff out but didn't want any lasting effects while you worked it out, go for it - you
                           can delete campaigns, journals, entries and individual user stories all individually now.
                        </div><br></td>
