                        <h1><a name="1919"></a><a href="/readMore.html?id=1919">Campaigns Support is Up</a></h1>
                        <div class="ItemInfo">Posted on
                           2004-04-18 at
                           06:21:50,
                           <a href="/readMore.html?id=1919">0 messages in 0 threads.</a> Last comment on 18/04/04.
                        </div>
                        <div>Feel like sharing your campaigns with everyone? Or perhaps you want a diary space that you can have for you and your players
                           to keep track of what is going on in your campaign? Perhaps you are playtesting something for Earthdawn Classic and you want
                           to record what happens (members only!). Check out out our new Campaigns section - it even has <b>help</b>. Please feel free to provide feedback in the Web comments forum, if there are other things you need.
                        </div><br></td>
